summary: An ordinance providing for the cost and expense of the laying off, opening, widening, extending and establishing of Tenth Avenue Northeast over and across a portion of block five (5), Brooklyn Addition to the City of Seattle, and block two (2), Supplemental Addition of McGuire and Holden's Addition to Latona, now a portion of the City of Seattle, as a public street and highway, as provided in Ordinance No. 40027, of the City of Seattle, by the issuance and sale of bonds by the district created to pay therefor.
